{{Infobox video game |title = TV Tycoon |image = |developer = Niels Bauer Games |publisher = eGames |designer = Niels Bauer |released = July 9, 2001 |genre = [[Business simulation game]] |modes = [[Single-player]] |platforms = PC }}
'''''TV Tycoon''''' is a [[computer game]] by [[EGames (video game developer)|eGames]]. It simulates managing a [[TV station]], making money by selling [[advertising]] space, and avoiding [[bankruptcy]]. Although eGames has been selling the game, it actually was originally created by [[Niels Bauer]] and was previously available as TV Manager.
